context.name: По_месяцу_и_офису
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance)
WHERE (udm:(Schedule:attendance.month) = :месяц AND udm:(Schedule:attendance.office_name) = :офис)

context.name: По_месяцу
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:calendar_dates)
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:calendar_dates.date)) = :месяц

context.name: по_дням
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord)
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.date)) = :месяц
AND udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.office_name) = :офис
order by udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.date)

context.name: загруженность
context.sql:
SELECT udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.day) as day,
count(*) as kolichestvo
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord)
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.date)) = :месяц
AND udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.office_name) = :офис
AND udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.day) = :день
AND udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.status_name) = :статус
group by udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.day)

context.name: по_назв_офиса_и_мес
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_conflicts)
WHERE udm:(Schedule:attendance_conflicts.office_name) = :офис
AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_conflicts.date)) = :месяц

context.name: По_месяцу
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:vacations)
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:vacations.date_from)) = :месяц OR EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:vacations.date_to)) = :месяц

context.name: По_сотруднику_и_месяцу
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance)
WHERE (udm:(Schedule:attendance.month) = :месяц AND udm:(Schedule:attendance.employee) = :сотрудник)

context.name: по_офису_и_месяцу
context.sql:
SELECT *
FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord)
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.date)) = :месяц AND udm:(Schedule:attendance_dashbord.office_name) = :офис
